datoCmsEvent.title: Queering The Canon: a Ring of Keys Benefit Concert

featuredImage.alt: Poster for Queering the Canon event. Text reads: "Ring of Keys presents Queering the Canon: a benefit concert for our 2nd birthday. Joe's Pub, February 16, 7pm. 426 Lafayette Street. publictheater.org"

children.value: Announcing our benefit concert this FEBRUARY 16TH at Joe’s Pub 🔑🌈💃🏿 queered canon songs + new original songs written by queer writers in response to canon tunes = QUEERING THE CANON!
